g.title: _p_main_reconnecting_initial->_p_main_reconnecting_trying_connect
g.text: after(100 ms)/add_message("trying to connect to server " + get_server(curr_server),"info") ^network.connect

g.title: _p_main_reconnecting_trying_connect->_p_main_reconnecting_initial
g.text: after(5 s)/add_message("unable to connect to server " + get_server(curr_server),"info")

g.title: _p_main_disconnected_initial->_p_main_disconnected_trying_connect
g.text: after(100 ms)/add_message("trying to connect to server " + get_server(curr_server),"info") ^network.connect

g.title: _p_main_disconnected_trying_connect->_p_main_disconnected_initial
g.text: after(5 s)/add_message("unable to connect to server " + get_server(curr_server),"info")⁏ curr_server = (curr_server + 1) % get_nr_of_servers()⁏
